Creating a Custom User Model

user:
ID -> PK 
username -> varchar(25)
email -> varchar(1000)
phone_number -> varchar(20)
password -> varchar(100)

order:
ID -> PK
size -> varchar(1) ['small','medium','large','extra-large']
order_status -> varchar(1) ['pending', 'istransit', 'delivered']
flavour -> varchar(100)
quantity -> Integer 
created_at -> Datetime
updated_at -> Datetime
user_id -> FK

